Introduction

Gyeongree is a South Korean actress, model, and singer under YNK Entertainment. She is a former member of 9MUSES and the co-ed group Nasty Nasty.

In 2010, Gyeongree worked as a backup dancer for Chae Yeon. The same year, Gyeongree signed under Star Empire Entertainment as a trainee and was featured on Mnet's reality show "Children of the Empire". As of July 31, 2019, Gyeongree decided to not renew her contract with the agency, later signing with YNK Entertainment in January 2020 promoting under her full name.

On July 5, 2018, Gyeongree made her solo debut with her digital single "Blue Moon".
